snippet.title: Alex Warren & ROSÉ - On My Mind (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Alex Warren & ROSÉ - On My Mind out now: https://alexwarren.lnk.to/OnMyMind

Order limited 7” vinyl & CD single: https://alexwarren.lnk.to/omm-7in

Lyrics:
Hidden underneath the floor
In the attic of my dreams there’s somebody, I adore
I could smile, I could lie
say I never think about you at all
Most of the time

Maybe
It’s the way the clouds are painted
A perfect shade of yellow, all across the sky
Or maybe
It’s the way the times are changing, and I’m stuck in the middle
Frozen in a fire
But, baby, you’re on my mind
Ooh, ooh, ooh
Ooh, ooh, ooh

Doors will open, doors will close
In the basement of my dreams there’s somebody, I ignore (mmm)
I’m a fool, don’t be surprised
I don’t ever think about you at all
But right now I just need you to know

Maybe
It’s the way the clouds are painted
A perfect shade of yellow, all across the sky
Or maybe
It’s the way the times are changing, and I’m stuck in the middle
Frozen in a fire
But, baby, you’re on my mind
Ooh, ooh, ooh
Ooh, ooh, ooh

You showed up, crystal and casually
Our love, was what it had to be
You showed up, like you’re still attached to me
Our love, was what it had to be (had to be x2)

Maybe
It’s the way the clouds are painted
A perfect shade of yellow, all across the sky
Or maybe
It’s the way the times are changing, and I’m stuck in the middle
Frozen in a fire
But, baby, you’re on my mind (you’re on)
(you’re on)
Ooh, (you’re on) ooh, ooh (you’re on)
(you’re on)
Ooh, (you’re on) ooh, ooh (you’re on)
(you’re on)
(But) baby, you’re on my mind

snippet.title: 24hs siendo papás primerizos💘 / pediatra + vacunas 2 meses
snippet.description:
👶✨ ¡24 HORAS SIENDO PAPÁS PRIMERIZOS! 🍼💥

En este video te mostramos cómo vivimos un día completo como papás primerizos: desde la visita al pediatra hasta el momento de las vacunas de los 2 meses 😢💉 (¡sí, sufrimos más nosotros que él!).
Nos reímos, nos emocionamos y también nos estresamos un poquito… pero todo vale la pena por verlo crecer sano y feliz 💛

Si te gusta ver la realidad sin filtros, acompañarnos en esta etapa y crecer junto a nosotros, suscribite al canal y activá la campanita 🔔 ¡Así no te perdés nada de esta locura hermosa que es la paternidad!

📌 Dejá tu comentario contándonos cómo fue tu experiencia como mamá o papá primerizo y con las vacunas!. ¡Nos encanta leerl@s!

#PapásPrimerizos #VacunasBebé #VidaEnFamilia #VlogFamiliar
